UPDATE price_history_locf AS phl
                        SET
                            ma_5 = updates.ma_5,
                            ma_60 = updates.ma_60,
                            ma_300 = updates.ma_300
                        FROM (
                            SELECT *
                            FROM unnest($1::timestamptz[], $2::float8[], $3::float8[], $4::float8[])
                            AS t(time, ma_5, ma_60, ma_300)
                        ) AS updates
                        WHERE phl.time = updates.time
